Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出現在我面前的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.23,0:01:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅世之徒——拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.80,0:01:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他告之我弗利安格內所策劃的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稱為「都食」的恐怖計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,池
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都會從這世界上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被這份強烈的恐懼感所驅使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道此時的夏娜正被逼迫做出突然的決斷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞拉斯托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛才說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.68,0:02:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說去破壞密斯提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.53,0:02:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近幾日我們的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無謂的被那個牽制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.74,0:02:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是為了引出弗利安格內所需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就現在的情況來看百害而無一利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽和其他人都會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止人類
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如「都食」這個名字一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會將城市的一切都吞食進去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.19,0:03:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轉換成存在之力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.28,0:03:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能讓他得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.55,0:03:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就做你能力所及的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天學校見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.99,0:03:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是去做只有他能做到的事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能只是很細微的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:59.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也是他在這裡存在的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜  一定要通知夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要進行計劃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可愛的瑪莉安努
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好選不選
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是那個專吃火炬的「撿骨師」來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狀況迫在眉睫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是「都食」發動需要很長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中途被火霧戰士襲擊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人也會有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是多麼的溫柔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.29,0:04:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪莉安努
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.01,0:04:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經有對策了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:04.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在「都食」發動期間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為了使它不被打斷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.02,0:05:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會去和炎發灼眼的小矮子戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悼詞朗誦者則會去盯著自己的獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這片活動的「撿骨師」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一邊追著這氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊和小矮子對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要等待時機來到便行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這鈴搖響幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這城市中布下的鑰匙便會由線連結起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.23,0:05:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此一來所獲得的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪莉安努
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就會變成永遠的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:06:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起獲得永恆了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.75,0:06:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是拉米的判斷的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該可以相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火炬數量的異常增多也能理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.64,0:06:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做誘餌也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把弗利安格內引出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快解決掉那傢伙的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽和大家都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛一聲不吭的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火炬的話你都不打算好好聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽…媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小悠的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:00.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫小夏娜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要和小悠和睦相處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.89,0:07:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要這麼稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天做的是小悠最喜歡的蛋包飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早點回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏娜再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是…同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是火霧戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是這樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某種意義上和火炬是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在說什麼「只是」了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說的明明是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼續剛才的話說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:42.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好幾次  好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好幾次都被這種無法平靜的心情給
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封絕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.07,0:07:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要用這個名字來叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是火霧戰士而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:12.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這…！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.49,0:08:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗利安格內
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:36.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到你會自己跑出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不用費周折也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話希望有句感謝的話語啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:53.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小矮子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天沒和那個密斯提斯在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要揣著明白裝糊塗了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是失敬了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小矮子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.49,0:09:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在和弗利安格內戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能交給夏娜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但現在的你真的能說是作為坂井悠二而活著的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:09:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只做現在的你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只做現在的你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.36,0:10:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能看見火炬而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我引以為傲的寶具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泡影鎖鏈的滋味如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管這劍是多麼的鋒利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不可能切斷的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就切斷根源
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜  退後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:10:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你非常想讓我奪走寶具呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中間到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火霧戰士竟然會止住刀刃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想拿回這個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就來追我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會準備好最棒的舞台等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心裡有數就是指啟作的家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.35,0:11:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙因為某些原因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:12:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在這大屋子裡一個人住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你原來是有錢人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真讓人嫉妒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正中下懷啊  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不會很麻煩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩親和社會性之類的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩親也不會說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,評價也不會比現在更差了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大…大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,御崎市  地圖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.87,0:12:35.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在這城市裡布下了自在式的網
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算拉米想要逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就會探知到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣  要喝了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是  馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小矮子還真慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該沒可能會在那雜亂的爆炸中給吹跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜是火霧戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會來打倒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火霧戰士還真是可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被使命所束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被紅世之王所束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也無法逃脫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是值得同情的存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不記得選了條被同情的路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用快攻  解決掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.77,0:14:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥方式太直接了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:36.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法助夏娜一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只做現在的你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜正在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全幫不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該有什麼能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜  後面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用踢的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來在操場上也不是鬧著玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要集中精神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以看清光球的運動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少要把這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜  後面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.77,0:15:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正上方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  吵死了  吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體變靈活了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且總感到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火焰的威力在上升
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求您了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:49.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.94,0:15:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的  瑪莉安努
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在此是不能退卻的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歷經艱辛所安置的永恆的基石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以為了這種事就放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.04,0:16:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上「都食」就開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要撐到那時就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬爾克西亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.79,0:16:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.92,0:16:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那戀物癖混蛋正準備幹些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種狀況下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算布了網
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.94,0:16:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒辦法探知到拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪邊都搞不定了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點我們的自在式就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.80,0:17:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請平安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火霧戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.07,0:17:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.57,0:17:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可愛的瑪莉安努
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上願望就能實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼那些光球消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.22,0:18:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴卻還在響
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要把夏娜引到這麼高的屋頂上來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道那傢伙為了隱藏這個才把夏娜引到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.81,0:18:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「都食」難道已經開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時機已經到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上我們所祈望的「都食」就會開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在這之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把她解決掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:37.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是作為區區一個討伐的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然敢冒犯我們的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.48,0:18:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然要用幸福扳機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs20}幸福扳機：火霧戰士必殺道具  瞬間激發契約者「王」沉睡的力量\N以達到使作為容器的火霧戰士承受不了太過強大的力量而爆裂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就拿走你的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:06.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會拿走全部的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.32,0:19:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也想見識下「都食」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏…夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為我們所獲得的永恆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是祝福的禮炮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪莉安努
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:20.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起來  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了  小矮子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為我們帶來永恆的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:19:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和瑪莉安努成為永恆的儀式不會完結的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會完結
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:14.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備打到何時啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好看著吧  瑪莉安努
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會獲得永恆的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.56,0:20:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪莉安努
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是….
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永恆的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為聽到你的聲音才站起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫上忙真高興
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存在之力被吸掉好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經是快消失的命運了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.74,0:21:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只是個火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是太勉強自己了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說什麼「只是」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.85,0:21:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是坂井悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:33.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天是因為我才輸了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才想砍我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.67,0:21:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.72,0:21:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.05,0:21:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.08,0:21:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微有了些在這裡的意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了  夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.28,0:22:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.31,0:22:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來沒錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是在你體內的寶具
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.16,0:22:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅世秘寶中的秘寶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.70,0:22:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,零時迷子的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.78,0:22:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一天內所消耗的存在之力會在深夜零時完全回復哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.08,0:22:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.56,0:22:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是說你還有未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.52,0:22:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是打擾到你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.26,0:22:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要對剛才的事道聲謝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.52,0:22:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.56,0:22:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你們打得不耐煩了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.84,0:22:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  戳到你痛處了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.70,0:22:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算和你以後好好打一場的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.51,0:22:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.50,0:24:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於紅世之徒的憎恨而追逐著拉米的瑪裘莉·頓
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.34,0:24:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為火霧戰士挺身而出的夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.24,0:24:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人又再次開戰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.54,0:24:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.43,0:24:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個火霧戰士
